        <Parent_String>roofs by form: exterior shape [300002103], roofs by form [300131140], roofs [300002098], roofs and roof components [300052266], enclosing structural elements [300078050], structural elements [300078048], structural elements and components for structural elements [300078046], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
